  "body": "### Description\r\n# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nEdit option changes message format.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Write a formated text in the chat input field\r\n2. Send message\r\n3. Edit message and save\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nWhen Edit option is open, text keeps the format and it is possible to add text with format.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nWhen Edit option is open, text format is removed and _sometimes_ it is not possible to save text with format.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/194479000-d6425bb2-99ee-4ea2-aec6-cda4cb16c7a9.mov\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.7.0-rc.4 and master `5c3517ee6f51fbcccc6bcf07c2b4daf0bbfdfe23`\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n\r\n",
